  "description": "Ocelot's wildness index maps inversely onto Ouroboros's Leash parameter — the more feral the predator, the more the strange attractor escapes constraint. At rest the leash holds the attractor on a short loop; at full prowl the attractor spirals into unbound chaos. The predator unleashes the mathematics. VelocityToTimbre coupling keeps the chaos responsive to playing intensity.",
